{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-archived-blog-template-js","path":"/2013/06/use-magic-lantern/","result":{"data":{"archivedBlogPostJson":{"categories":[{"path":"/category/learn/","name":"摄影学习与折腾"},{"path":"/category/film/","name":"独立电影与短片"}],"tags":[{"name":"Magic Lantern","path":"/tag/magic-lantern/"},{"name":"佳能","path":"/tag/canon-camera/"},{"name":"固件","path":"/tag/firmware/"},{"name":"城市","path":"/tag/city/"},{"name":"夜景","path":"/tag/night-scene/"},{"name":"摄影","path":"/tag/photography/"}],"featured_media":{"source_url":"https://archived-blog.berlinchan.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/06/MG_6465-Panorama_.jpg"},"path":"/2013/06/use-magic-lantern/","date":"2013-06-09T09:39:02.000Z","excerpt":"为宜昌华祥商业中心拍摄一组关于它们项目的夜景风光照片。 户外的夜景拍摄要关注的时机很重要，当中包括了天气、日落 … ","title":"巧用Magic Lantern拍摄城市夜景风光-一个拍摄案例","content":"<p>为宜昌华祥商业中心拍摄一组关于它们项目的夜景风光照片。</p>\n<p>户外的夜景拍摄要关注的时机很重要，当中包括了天气、日落时间、日落方向，需要提前做好功课。这次夜景拍摄结合了长时间曝光和全景接片。为了达到稳定触发快门的目的，在没有快门线的情况下，我们使用了Canon的破解固件Magic Lantern中的声音遥控快门功能，当然牢固的三脚架必不可少。</p>\n<p><object width=\"480\" height=\"400\" classid=\"clsid:d27cdb6e-ae6d-11cf-96b8-444553540000\" codebase=\"http://download.macromedia.com/pub/shockwave/cabs/flash/swflash.cab#version=6,0,40,0\" align=\"middle\"><param name=\"src\" value=\"http://player.youku.com/player.php/sid/XNTY1MjgzNzg4/v.swf\" /><param name=\"allowfullscreen\" value=\"true\" /><param name=\"quality\" value=\"high\" /><param name=\"allowscriptaccess\" value=\"always\" /><embed width=\"480\" height=\"400\" type=\"application/x-shockwave-flash\" src=\"//player.youku.com/player.php/sid/XNTY1MjgzNzg4/v.swf\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" quality=\"high\" allowscriptaccess=\"always\" align=\"middle\" /></object></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=7rihYsC-K8I\" target=\"_blank\">在YouTube上观看</a></p>\n<p>有的朋友看了后对这个MagicLantern（<a href=\"http://www.magiclantern.fm/\" target=\"_blank\">项目官网www.magiclantern.fm</a>）固件感兴趣了，这个项目充分挖掘了佳能的数字单反性能。以后来出一个安装和使用MagicLantern的介绍，请关注。</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://archived-blog.berlinchan.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/06/MG_6465-Panorama_.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1298\" alt=\"华祥商业中心夜景\" src=\"https://archived-blog.berlinchan.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/06/MG_6465-Panorama_-300x142.jpg\" width=\"489\" height=\"231\" srcset=\"https://archived-blog.berlinchan.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/06/MG_6465-Panorama_-300x142.jpg 300w, https://archived-blog.berlinchan.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/06/MG_6465-Panorama_-1024x485.jpg 1024w, https://archived-blog.berlinchan.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/06/MG_6465-Panorama_-624x295.jpg 624w, https://archived-blog.berlinchan.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/06/MG_6465-Panorama_.jpg 1200w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 489px) 100vw, 489px\" /></a></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">宜昌华祥商业中心夜景</p>\n"}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/2013/06/use-magic-lantern/"}},"staticQueryHashes":["251939775","3675143411","4019104361"]}